&lt;div class=&quot;content-intro&quot;&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WHY JOIN ALO?&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Mindful movement. It’s at the core of why we do what we do at ALO—it’s our calling. Because mindful movement in the studio leads to better living. It changes who yogis are off the mat, making their lives and their communities better. That’s the real meaning of studio-to-street: taking the consciousness from practice on the mat and putting it into practice in life.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h3 data-start=&quot;119&quot; data-end=&quot;133&quot;&gt;Overview&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Alo is seeking a visionary &lt;strong&gt;3D Technical Designer&lt;/strong&gt; to lead the digital evolution of our garment development process. This role is at the intersection of traditional craftsmanship and cutting-edge technology. You will be responsible for procuring high-fidelity 3D garment assemblies, collaborating with Fit Technicians to perfect silhouettes, and translating digital files into production-ready assets.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate possesses a rare blend of technical engineering and artistic instinct, allowing them to optimize garment construction for both economic efficiency and the iconic &quot;alo fit.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;
