&lt;ul data-start=&quot;839&quot; data-end=&quot;2336&quot;&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;839&quot; data-end=&quot;1046&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;841&quot; data-end=&quot;1046&quot;&gt;Execute advanced 3D prototypes in CLO based on Technical Design Block direction from the Director of Technical Design, ensuring garments accurately reflect construction, drape, and performance standards.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1047&quot; data-end=&quot;1180&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1049&quot; data-end=&quot;1180&quot;&gt;Serve as the primary administrator for CLO 3D and the CLO-SET environment, maintaining platform integrity and digital governance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1181&quot; data-end=&quot;1344&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1183&quot; data-end=&quot;1344&quot;&gt;Manage and organize global digital libraries including fabrics, trims, blocks, avatars, and hardware, ensuring all assets meet quality and accuracy benchmarks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1345&quot; data-end=&quot;1491&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1347&quot; data-end=&quot;1491&quot;&gt;Support and evolve digital workflows to reduce physical sample waste while accelerating speed-to-market and increasing operational efficiency.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1492&quot; data-end=&quot;1624&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1494&quot; data-end=&quot;1624&quot;&gt;Assist in testing new digital tools and software enhancements, providing structured feedback and implementation recommendations.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1625&quot; data-end=&quot;1772&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1627&quot; data-end=&quot;1772&quot;&gt;Define and maintain quality standards for all 3D assets, including fabric scan accuracy, trim digitization, and garment simulation performance.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1773&quot; data-end=&quot;1919&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1775&quot; data-end=&quot;1919&quot;&gt;Drive reduction in physical sample iterations through high-fidelity digital prototypes, building a scalable and sustainable digital ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;1920&quot; data-end=&quot;2070&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;1922&quot; data-end=&quot;2070&quot;&gt;Monitor CLO fit notes in collaboration with Technical Designers and Fit Experts, producing refined 3D assets for review by Technical Fit Advisors.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li data-start=&quot;2071&quot; data-end=&quot;2191&quot;&gt;
&lt;p data-start=&quot;2073&quot; data-end=&quot;2191&quot;&gt;Manage PLM data pull requests regarding specs, style history, and

