&lt;li&gt;Experience working in the apparel, ecommerce, or related industry (public/private) is a plus.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Ability to execute deadline driven processes in a dynamic environment.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Excellent oral and written communication skills, with the ability to convey information to internal and external customers in a clear, focused and concise manner.&lt;/li&gt;
