&lt;li&gt;10+ years of experience in ERP, Merch and Planning systems with increasing Functional and Technical responsibilities&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Extensive experience and In depth knowledge of the functionality of ERP Finance and Supply chain (Direct purchasing &amp;amp; Inventory)&lt;/li&gt;
